HospitalPages.ie ChangeLog

Version 0.0.3

27-May-2009
- Created migration files for all tables in db structure
- Added default hospital image
- Created Admin section for adding new information
   # Uses basic http authentication for now

25-May-2009
- Added static frontpage with basic search box
- Integrated header and footer to layout
- Added non functional links to desired static pages (about, contact etc)
- Tidied up migration scripts
- Added Region (will be used for County in Ireland)
- Added example tag line (The Central Directory for Hospital Information in Ireland)
- Integrated Blueprint CSS plugin for buttons
